      {"@type": "Question", "name": "Acoperiti zona Dristor complet?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Da — acoperim tot cartierul Dristor, de la intersectia cu Calea Vacaresti pana la limita cu Titan si Dudestu. Transport inclus in orice punct."}},
