      {"@type": "Question", "name": "Cat costa un animator in zona Dristor?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "De la 490 RON (Super 1, 2 ore, 1 personaj). Fara taxa de deplasare in Dristor, Vitan sau Titan."}},
